Here's the PlantUML component diagram for the Cima+ iOS application:

```plantuml
@startuml kerollesroshdi_Cima-

package "Domain Layer" {
    [Entities] as Entities
    [UseCases] as UseCases
    [Repositories] as DomainRepositories
}

package "Data Layer" {
    [RemoteDataSources] as RemoteDataSources
    [RepositoriesImpl] as DataRepositories
}

package "App Layer" {
    [ViewControllers] as ViewControllers
    [ViewModels] as ViewModels
    [Coordinators] as Coordinators
    [UI Components] as UIComponents
}

[TMDB API] as TMDB

Entities --> UseCases : contains
DomainRepositories --> UseCases : depends on

DataRepositories --> RemoteDataSources : uses
RemoteDataSources --> TMDB : fetches from
DataRepositories ..|> DomainRepositories : implements

ViewModels --> UseCases : depends on
ViewModels --> DataRepositories : depends on
ViewControllers --> ViewModels : observes
Coordinators --> ViewControllers : manages
UIComponents --> ViewControllers : used by

@enduml
```